---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Portfolio"
  description="The Poesis portfolio: the GSM open standard, the SIE engine, the ITIP application, the SAFe Agentic Framework, and the transformation services around them."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio</p>
      <h1>One standard, one engine, one application.</h1>
      <p class="lead">The pieces compose top to bottom: GSM defines the meaning, SIE runs it, ITIP applies it to IT, the framework generates from it, and services deliver the change.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag">Standard</span>
          <h3>GSM</h3>
          <p>The Generative System Model — the open, vendor-neutral standard for defining and governing systems.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/standard">About GSM →</a> &middot; <a href="https://docs.poesis.cloud/gsm/">Docs</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud/gsm">Repo</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Engine</span>
          <h3>SIE</h3>
          <p>The Systemic Intelligence Engine — hosts GSM, enforces its lifecycle, and powers the domain applications above it.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/sie">About SIE →</a> &middot; <a href="https://docs.poesis.cloud/sie-definition/">Docs</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud">Repos</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Application</span>
          <h3>ITIP</h3>
          <p>The IT Intelligence Platform — the first domain application, governing the IT landscape as a single source of truth.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/itip">About ITIP →</a> &middot; <a href="https://docs.poesis.cloud/itip/">Docs</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud">Repos</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag--muted">Framework</span>
          <h3>SAFe Agentic Framework</h3>
          <p>The open (Apache-2.0) BUILD layer that turns governed definitions into runnable code.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:.6rem"><a href="/framework">About the framework →</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud/safe-agentic-framework">Repo</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Bring it to your organization.</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-inline:auto">The transformation services deploy the whole stack as the governed substrate of your change.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/services">See the services →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

